OL,3,CThree arrested following attempted
OL,4,Carson attack in Wembley
OL,6,FThree men have been arrested following
OL,7,Fan attempted arson attack on the
OL,8,Foffices of a Persian language media
OL,9,Forganisation in north-west London.
OL,11,FAn ignited container was thrown
OL,12,Ftowards the premises at around 8.30pm
OL,13,Fon Wednesday, Metropolitan Police has
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FThe container landed in a car park,
OL,17,Fand the fire immediately put itself
OL,18,Fout. No injuries or damage were
OL,19,Freported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
