OL,3,CThree arrested following attempted
OL,4,Carson attack in Wembley
OL,6,FOfficers on patrol in the area
OL,7,Festablished that the suspects had left
OL,8,Fin a black SUV.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FA 16-year-old boy and two men aged 19
OL,16,Fand 21 were arrested on suspicion of
OL,17,Farson endangering life and were taken
OL,18,Finto police custody where they remain
OL,19,Fas of Thursday afternoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
