OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776423773
OL,3,CThree arrested following attempted
OL,4,Carson attack in Wembley
OL,6,FPolice said a number of buildings
OL,7,Fnearby were evacuated "as a
OL,8,Fprecaution" but it was quickly
OL,9,Festablished "there was no wider risk".
OL,11,F"The attack is not being treated as a
OL,12,Fterrorist incident but is being
OL,13,Finvestigated by detectives from
OL,14,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,15,Fsupported by officers from the North
OL,16,FWest Command Area," Metropolitan
OL,17,FPolice said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
