OL,3,CThree arrested following attempted
OL,4,Carson attack in Wembley
OL,6,FThe attack came after recent arson
OL,7,Fincidents in London, one on a
OL,8,Fsynagogue in Finchley this week, and
OL,9,Fthe other on ambulances in Golders
OL,10,FGreen. The Met Police has said the
OL,11,Fattacks are not currently being linked.
OL,13,F"At this stage, it is not being linked
OL,14,Fto the attempted arson in Finchley
OL,15,Fthis week or last month's arson in
OL,16,FGolders Green," the statement read.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
