OL,3,CThree arrested following attempted
OL,4,Carson attack in Wembley
OL,6,F"While all three incidents are being
OL,7,Ftreated as separate incidents, the
OL,8,Fsimilarity with all three being
OL,9,Farsons, and the nature of the
OL,10,Fbuildings and locations of the
OL,11,Fincidents has been factored into the
OL,12,Fdecision for CTP London to investigate
OL,13,Fall three incidents," a statement from
OL,14,FCounter Terrorism Policing said.
